    <div class="section">
      

<div id="review_4046746746" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4046746746" />
    <a title="David" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/30564033-david"><img alt="David" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/m_50x66-82093808bca726cb3249a493fbd3bd0f.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4046746746?book_show_action=true">Jun 12, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="David" class="user" itemprop="url" name="David" href="/user/show/30564033-david">David</a>
      </span>

          added it


          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781476704500" href="/book/show/15800644-the-heather-blazing">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/30564033-david?shelf=new-in-2021">new-in-2021</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4046746746" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17000829260962450495">A very quietly sad book, which painstakingly and sometimes painfully delineates the life of a man who preserves himself from all emotional injury by more or less freezing off his emotions. He lives by the letter of the law, literally and figuratively. He is alive, but one cannot help wondering what kind of a life it is. Nature imagery, erosion, swimming in the ocean, changing clothing – all are plentiful in the narrative and both symbolic and literal. Not an easy read, but worth the time. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

